O ye who believe! What aileth you that when it is said unto you： Go
forth in the way of Allâh, ye are bowed down to the ground with
heaviness. Take ye pleasure in the life of the world rather than in
the Hereafter? The comfort of the life of the world is but little in
the Hereafter.
